VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(?:system|exec|spawn|popen|Open3\.(?:capture2e?|pipeline|popen2e?))\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:Shellwords\.escape|Shellwords\.shellescape|validate|sanitize|allowlist && MISSING:test|spec|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects shell command execution APIs in Ruby that can be dangerous when fed untrusted input.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Unsafe Shell Command Execution.
